{"word":"G4846 - συμπνίγω - sympnígō - soom-pnee'-go - Choke","slug":"G4846","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπνίγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sympnígō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soom-pnee'-go"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Choke"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03C0;&#x03BD;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03C9; - sumpnigo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soom-pnee'-go</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4155\">G4155</a>; to <i>strangle completely</i>, that is, (literally) to <i>drown</i>, or (figuratively) to <i>crowd:</i> - choke, throng."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4155\">G4155</a>, <a href=\"#/G4156\">G4156</a>, <a href=\"#/G638\">G638</a>"}]}